Description: 64Kb intro by The Black Lotus (1997)
 Stash is a 64 Kb intro released by The Black Lotus at a demoparty in 1997.
 It delivers 3.5 MB of full-colour graphics and 4 MB of music sampled at
 16-bit/44 kHz, packed into a 64 Kb executable.
 .
 Created by probe, jace, nix, balance, danny, and sick1/trp, the production
 requires a Pentium-class CPU, a VGA card, and a Gravis UltraSound with at
 least 1 MB of sample RAM.
